title: Hunger Games Mokingjay Part 2
text:
Home / Movies / Hunger Games Mokingjay Part 2 Hunger Games Mokingjay Part 2 By International_d on October 16, 2015 1 share 


The next chapter in the Hunger Games frenzy will be in theaters for your Thanksgiving Day The Hunger Games: Mockingjay part II , starring Jennifer Lawrence, Josh Hutcherson, Liam Hemsworth, Elizabeth Banks, Woody Harrelson, and Julianne Moore, opens courtesy of Lions Gate Entertainment on November 20th, 2015 in 2D, 3D, and IMAX 3D. Kat is back to unite the people against the powers that be. Mokingjay Part 2 is action packed and full of twists that you will not believe. Mark it on your calendars to see this movie.
